high_descs: Turn to your right and approach the counter.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn to your left approach the counter next to the stove.
Place the sponge in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl on the counter.
Walk to the dishwasher to the right.
place the bowl in the cupboard to the left of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl in the cupboard to the left of the dishwasher.

high_descs: Walk towards the oven, then turn right and walk up to where the toaster is on the counter.
Pick up the sponge off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the sponge in the glass bowl on the counter.
Pick up the glass bowl with the sponge in it.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left and take another step, turn left to face the dishwasher.
Open the cabinet door to the left of the dishwasher and put the glass bowl with the sponge in it in the cabinet, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass bowl with a sponge in it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the sponge on the counter.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn left, bring the sponge to the bowl on the counter.
Put the sponge in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl with sponge from on the counter.
Bring the the bowl to the lower left cabinet under the toaster.
Put the bowl in the lower left cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with sponge in a cabinet.
